        <briefdescription>
<para>Adds configuration sources to the IHostBuilder. This includes loading environment variables, JSON configuration files, and setting the base directory for the configuration. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>hostBuilder</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The IHostBuilder instance to configure.</para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>The configured IHostBuilder instance.</para>
</simplesect>
</para>
<para>This method will configure the application to load: <itemizedlist>
<listitem>
<para>Environment variables with a prefix of &quot;PREFIX_&quot; </para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<para>appsettings.json (if it exists) </para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<para>appsettings.{environmentName}.json (where environmentName is derived from the CORE_ENVIRONMENT environment variable, defaulting to &quot;Development&quot;) </para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<para>All environment variables </para>
</listitem>
</itemizedlist>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
